    <string name="about_text">\n
        The \"New formula\" is from the paper
        <i>\"A reliable game fish weight estimation model for Atlantic Tarpon (Megalops Atlanticus)\"</i>
        (Ault and Luo, 2013)\n\n
        The \"Old formula\" is the classic (and quite inaccurate) \n
        <i>weight = length * girth * girth / 800</i>\n(inches, pounds)\n\n

        This app is Free Software. The code is at https://github.com/oggust/tarpon-calculator.git\n
        If you want to donate anything, donate it to the Bonefish &amp; Tarpon Trust (BTT).\n
        http://www.bonefishtarpontrust.org\n\n
        Bugs? Feature requests? I\'m oggust@gmail.com</string>

